  ["<div style='min-width: 180px; min-height: 50px;'><h2 class='articleHeader'>Midway, US Pacific Islands</h2><div class='infowindowSubTitle'>25 Dec 1941</div>Carrier USS Saratoga launched F2A Buffalo aircraft of Marine Fighter Squadron 221, originally intended to relieve Wake Atoll, to Midway Atoll.  They became the first fighters to be based in Midway, and they immediately began a daily patrol schedule.<br /><div class='infowindowSubTitle'>25 Jun 1942</div>Saratoga delivered 25 P-40 Warhawk fighters and 18 SBD Dauntless dive bombers to Midway Atoll.<br /></div>", 28.201389000, 182.618611, 2],
